Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.46,0:17:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪  已經足足24小時了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jesus, it's been a full 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.35,0:17:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們能去哪呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where the hell could they be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.79,0:17:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有止痛藥嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Got any Advil?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.61,0:17:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒去聯系中國那邊嘍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm guessing you didn't make contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.33,0:17:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能這個計劃太大了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps this plan was a little too ambitious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們先等其他人回來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll wait until the rest of them get back
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后重新評估情況\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and then reevaluate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.88,0:17:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無能為力地坐在這兒  等著完蛋嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sitting here helpless while we crash and burn?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.98,0:17:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我的風格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not my speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.48,0:17:39.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使他們黑進了鋼山\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even if they hack into steel mountain,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也要同時攻擊中國的數據中心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we need to hit China's data centers simultaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果黑暗軍團不照做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If the Dark Army isn't compliant,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.92,0:17:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們也無能為力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then there's not much we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天...該死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}God... Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喝大了  都忘了今天是周日\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got so wasted, I forgot it's Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.61,0:17:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我的人在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know where my guy will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:56.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that wise?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.87,0:17:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些人可不怎么體諒人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those guys aren't known for being the most understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.94,0:18:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他想聯系我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm assuming if he wanted contact--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.06,0:18:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在是我想聯系他們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about what I want?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.78,0:18:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你一起去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm coming with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.16,0:18:08.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:11.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你待在這兒  等他們上FTP\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You stick around, wait for the boys to FTP it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.14,0:18:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特倫頓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, Trenton.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.36,0:18:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.41,0:18:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-這是什么  -就這最后兩顆了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What is this? - Come on, they're my last two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:48.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是搖頭丸嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is this ecstasy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.41,0:18:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  是"明白藥"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, it's clarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.83,0:18:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能讓你看明白你現在的煩惱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It'll help you see past whatever's bringing you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.92,0:18:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我不想無禮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry. I don't mean to be rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:18:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不吸毒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I...don't do drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是抽點大麻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, I-I smoke weed--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.81,0:19:03.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  但是不能還給我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, sorry, but there's no take-backs, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.73,0:19:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再說  難道你不想想明白你的心事嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Besides, don't you want to figure your shit out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.39,0:19:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時候  如果我遇到什么難事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For me, sometimes when I'm going through something,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就...怎么說呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just gotta--I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先忘卻它一陣子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forget about it for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是真在喝氣泡水吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you seriously drinking a goddamn sparkling water right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.09,0:20:01.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是你系著我的圍巾  我就揍你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you weren't wearing my scarf, I'd kick your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.81,0:20:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還是走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think we should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.25,0:20:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我  他每周日都來這兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Trust me--he's here every Sunday, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.65,0:20:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他會來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He'll show.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.84,0:20:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊  羅梅洛  我們該怎么辦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jesus Christ, Romero. What are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.81,0:20:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們把他扔到哪家醫院\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We dump him at a hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.71,0:20:25.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再想其他辦法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}come up with an alternative course of action.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.51,0:20:26.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我們唯一的選擇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's our only option.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.97,0:20:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  不能去醫院\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. No hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們就走人  管他呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then we split. Screw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:31.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己也總這么說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, you say it all the time yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.98,0:20:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次革命都要流血犧牲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there's casualties in every revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.97,0:20:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有結果是最重要的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All that matters is the end result.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們沒時間帶著累贅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We got no time to haul dead weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.66,0:20:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  你想走  走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fine! You wanna leave, leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.75,0:20:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Screw this, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:02.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得嗑一發\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need a hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會好起來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll be better.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我挺過去就行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just to get me through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.65,0:21:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能讓你那么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't let you do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.52,0:21:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就嗑一發\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.24,0:21:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能讓我重新上路就行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, just to get me back on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.45,0:21:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們沒時間了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't have time. This...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們得馬上行動\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}needs to happen now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.52,0:21:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一發\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.27,0:21:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}{\*}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.30,0:21:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.81,0:21:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾一下  伙計\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Excuse me, fella.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.45,0:21:43.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在找什么嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You lookin' for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.50,0:21:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他需要點幫助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He could really use a helping hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.60,0:21:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  他可以進去  但只能他一人進去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, okay, he can go in. But only him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.11,0:21:52.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  我也得進去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, no can do. I gotta come with.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.77,0:21:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非你也嗑  否則就只有他能進去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only if you're partaking, otherwise he goes it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.81,0:22:01.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.67,0:22:03.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,30塊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}30.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.35,0:22:05.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,30塊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}30.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.20,0:22:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屋里的人會照顧你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The guy in the house will set you up right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.40,0:22:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要他不殺你的話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Long as he doesn't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.19,0:22:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽著  你一嗑完\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, look, the minute you're done...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.77,0:22:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就馬上走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.13,0:22:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不許看任何人  也不許跟任何人說話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't look at anyone. You don't talk to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.40,0:22:26.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你辦完了事  就出來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You take care of business and you get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.41,0:22:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白就點點頭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nod if you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.28,0:23:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.65,0:23:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(100,300)\pos(294,7.2)}{\fn方正兰亭粗黑_GBK\fs16\fsp2\b0\bord2\shad0\3c&H20384B&\c&H000000&}去社會
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.84,0:23:07.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大眼睛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Big eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.52,0:23:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的  哥們  來吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all good, man. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.36,0:23:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.52,0:23:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要嗎啡  片劑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need morphine. Pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.74,0:23:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.45,0:23:20.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們這里只有這個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is all we got right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.76,0:23:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個更好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's better.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.62,0:23:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.04,0:23:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿著吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.40,0:23:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就對了  這就對了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There you go. There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.45,0:23:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我幫你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.63,0:23:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的  我幫你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It'll be okay. I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.66,0:23:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都墮落到這個地步了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have I sunk this low?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.49,0:23:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會怎么想我啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What must you think of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.47,0:23:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在是春天了嗎  大選年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it spring? Election year?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.21,0:23:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我該冬眠嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shall I hibernate?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.33,0:23:59.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們見過嗎  我們信任金錢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did we meet? In money we trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.75,0:24:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對  我創造了...停下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I created-- stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.64,0:24:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我無法控制思緒  我需要這個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't control thoughts. I need this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.13,0:24:09.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我保證過那是最后一條  但是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know I promised my last line, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.46,0:24:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.09,0:24:24.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要臉的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Greedy bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.81,0:24:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shit, man--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.26,0:24:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周三  周四  周五\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wednesday, Thursday, Friday,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.66,0:24:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以下是三州地區的七日預報\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}here's that seven-day forecast for the tri-state area.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.55,0:24:52.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今日多云  但周四基本晴朗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lots of clouds today, but mostly sunny through Thursday
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.57,0:24:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,氣溫偏高  可達26度多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with temperatures in the mid to the upper 80s.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.65,0:24:58.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且濕度會稍稍使人感到不適\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you will notice that the humidity will be a tad uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.80,0:24:57.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\frx24\fry354\pos(217.286,27.657)}{\fn方正兰亭粗黑_GBK\fsp2\fs11\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&HB8B8C8&}七日預報
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.06,0:25:01.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,親愛的兄弟姐妹們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dear brothers and sisters,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.52,0:25:03.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在該睜開眼睛了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}now is the time to open your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.32,0:25:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你尚未覺醒  看清現實中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you have not yet woken up to the reality of
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.35,0:25:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們所指出的不正當牟利和奴役\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}profiteering and enslavement we've been warning you about,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.36,0:25:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你明白  你很快就要沒時間了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hope you realize you are fast running out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.49,0:25:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界各國的政府和其大公司主人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The governments of the world and their corporate masters
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.73,0:25:17.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不希望我們發聲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}do not want us to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.46,0:25:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什么  因為我們挖掘真相\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why? Because we unlock truths.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.86,0:25:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們曝光惡人  我們處決惡魔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We expose villains. We exorcize demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.83,0:25:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界公民們  我們是來幫忙的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Citizens of the world, we are here to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.45,0:25:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你們想從沉睡中蘇醒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you have any interest in waking from your slumber,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.26,0:25:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想找回遺失  受損或被盜取的記憶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in retrieving lost, damaged, or stolen memory,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.38,0:25:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們會幫忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we are here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.78,0:25:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會照顧你  我們是去社會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have your back. We are fsociety.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.80,0:26:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是打開什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's it open?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.46,0:26:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在歸你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It belongs to you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.96,0:26:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠東制造\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Made in the orient.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.00,0:26:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,專為你的腦袋打造的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Made just for your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.04,0:26:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到你的怪物  轉動鑰匙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, find your monster, then turn the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.70,0:26:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但首先\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But first...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.81,0:26:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的公司財閥有話要說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a word from our corporate overlords!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.70,0:26:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果您看到了我們的標志  那代表您可以放心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}{\*}If you see our logo, that means you can rest assured
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.31,0:26:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您正在購買最優質的食品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that you're buying the best food,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.04,0:26:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衣物  居所\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}clothing, shelter,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.49,0:26:39.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交通工具  衛生設施  電器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}transportation, hygiene, electronics,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.90,0:26:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及其他生活必需品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and life's necessities that money can buy.
