Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.02,0:27:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.35,0:27:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello, friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.74,0:27:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我們不是朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we're not friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.01,0:27:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能告訴我這房子怎么了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you tell me what happened to that house?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.18,0:27:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先告訴我  你的怪物是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}First can you tell me? What's your monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.88,0:27:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是你掉的吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think you dropped this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.98,0:28:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別害羞嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't be shy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.94,0:28:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠近點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can come closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.53,0:28:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  令人不安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unsettling, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.00,0:28:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的寵物魚居然在跟你說話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your pet beta fish chatting you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.39,0:28:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但時間是金錢  艾略特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But time's money, Elliot.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.36,0:28:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要什么嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.35,0:28:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水需要換了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your water-- does it need changing?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.71,0:28:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生活在魚缸里  根本就沒什么"變"可言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When you live in a fishbowl, ain't no such thing as change.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.51,0:28:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這輩子一直待在這里面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My entire life's been spent in this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.80,0:29:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的整個世界就在你小桌上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My whole world's on your side table.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.93,0:29:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我環顧四周  每一天都一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I look around-- same shit, different day.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.08,0:29:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈光  家具\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The lighting, the furniture.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.97,0:29:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至聲音  總是一樣的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even the sounds-- always the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.82,0:29:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我處于循環之中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm on a loop,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.10,0:29:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非我死去  循環無法停止\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and it won't stop unless my life does.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.38,0:29:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受夠了這世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm exhausted with this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.01,0:29:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能做什么  我想幫忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What can I do? I wanna help.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.00,0:29:21.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得這很明顯吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think it's pretty obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.97,0:29:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也就只能為一只魚缸里的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's really only one thing you can do
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.97,0:29:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑魚做一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for a brother in a fishbowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.65,0:29:27.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.06,0:29:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他搬到窗邊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Move him to a goddamn window!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.67,0:29:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安吉拉  他是我的朋友啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Angela, he's my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.03,0:29:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.87,0:29:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很好吃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.18,0:29:57.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.22,0:30:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Eat this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.99,0:30:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,張嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Open.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.88,0:30:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常燙  吃的時候請小心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's piping hot, so consume with caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.66,0:30:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸著名的樹莓派  慢用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pop's famous raspberry pie. Enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.48,0:30:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.41,0:30:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.74,0:30:51.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意  艾略特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, Elliot, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.52,0:30:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾略特  我愿意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Elliot, I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.62,0:30:57.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.57,0:31:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛那些人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those people in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.39,0:31:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是說了他們想聽的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just told them what they wanted to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.49,0:32:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不會那么做的  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not gonna do it, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.78,0:32:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改變世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Change the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.13,0:32:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猜到了  你才一個月大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Figures. You were only born a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.97,0:32:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.45,0:32:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕你的怪物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Afraid of your monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.43,0:32:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道那是什么嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you even know what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.26,0:32:26.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不配套\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It doesn't fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.67,0:32:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.60,0:32:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這還不明顯嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.38,0:32:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是艾略特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not Elliot.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.62,0:32:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're the--
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.68,0:32:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.18,0:32:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.13,0:33:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是一個人嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Am I still alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.02,0:33:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我唯一的朋友的臉孔嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is this the face of my only friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.81,0:33:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的怪物嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you my monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.51,0:33:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在這兒  你是一個人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am here. You are alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.88,0:33:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們都走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They all left.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.21,0:33:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們都走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They all left.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.43,0:33:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是一個人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.03,0:33:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是一個人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.46,0:34:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是一個人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.64,0:34:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.82,0:34:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪都不會去的  孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not going anywhere, kiddo.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.07,0:34:17.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會一起走到底\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're in this to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.70,0:34:33.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還是好好走路吧  你似乎不太會跳芭蕾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}{\*}Maybe you should just walk. Ballet seems out of your skill set.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.84,0:34:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  去你的  小丫頭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What? Screw you, young'un!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.21,0:34:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老子的曲膝不比任何人差\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This bitch can plie with the best of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.43,0:34:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒忙著敲鍵盤的時候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, when I'm not bangin' on a keyboard,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.94,0:34:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在教同學這樣的舞步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm schooling classmates with moves like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.90,0:34:45.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天吶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.24,0:34:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝搭救\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good lookin' out.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.67,0:35:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遺憾他沒來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry he never came.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.82,0:35:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's--let's just go.
