Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.36,0:36:29.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么還在外面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why am I still out?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.83,0:36:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再過4小時  我就得去上班了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have to be at work - in four hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.31,0:36:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會十分懷念這份工作的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a lot I'm gonna miss about this gig.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.44,0:36:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今后要怎么掙錢啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you gonna do for money now?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.50,0:36:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是...去做個性感服務員唄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, you know. Just be a hottie waitress.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.09,0:36:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm, uh-- oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.28,0:36:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高興你喜歡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Glad you liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.34,0:36:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我很高興打工掙錢之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Although I am glad I got in one last hurrah
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.30,0:36:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還能再這么玩一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}before going all corporate.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.33,0:36:57.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不擔心嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.07,0:36:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擔心什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Worried about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.37,0:37:01.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說不清\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.29,0:37:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始新工作之前我總會很擔心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I always get worried before starting a new job.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.95,0:37:07.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我絕對不擔心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I am definitely not worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.55,0:37:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擔心是浪費時間\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Worry's a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.69,0:37:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這份工作不合適  我就另找一份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, shit didn't work out at one job, so I got another.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.86,0:37:13.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.04,0:37:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你經常擔心  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You worry a lot, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.96,0:37:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.24,0:37:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看鏡子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.84,0:37:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到那個狠角色了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See that badass bitch?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.45,0:38:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是你這輩子唯一該擔心的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's the only person you should ever worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.10,0:38:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我找你找得多辛苦嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know how hard it's been for me to find you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.52,0:38:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.95,0:38:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你冷靜點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yo, you need to chill.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.99,0:38:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧  混蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go to hell, asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.35,0:38:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這才像話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.49,0:38:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我黑暗空虛的生活中的一縷陽光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A ray of sunshine in the dark void of my existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.49,0:38:54.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真詩意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, poetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.95,0:38:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這不叫道歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But not an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.30,0:38:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不想道歉呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I ain't apologizing for shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.09,0:39:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為我甩了你嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, this is because I dumped your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.94,0:39:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴你  你要惹火我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For real? You're gonna start pissing me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.51,0:39:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉我想跟你共度一生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry I wanted to spend my life with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.93,0:39:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真混蛋死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What a monster I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.39,0:39:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有大事要發生了  西斯科\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Things are happening, Cisco.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.23,0:39:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們明天就得行動\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to go tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.38,0:39:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是唯一的機會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's our only shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.10,0:39:14.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就沒機會了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then you never had one.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.42,0:39:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說真的  達琳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I'm serious, Darlene.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.69,0:39:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些人不是鬧著玩的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These guys don't mess around.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.36,0:39:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你以為你在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, whatever it is you think you're doing--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.51,0:39:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解放世界  解救眾生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}freeing the world, freeing the masses--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.60,0:39:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雇我的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the guys I work for,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.48,0:39:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們的動機可不是那么高尚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they ain't motivated by kumbaya shit like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.16,0:39:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我警告你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right? Now, I'm warning you...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.70,0:39:31.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一次警告你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.43,0:39:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.51,0:39:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道這對我多重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know how much this means to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.50,0:40:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.83,0:40:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟他們談談\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.04,0:40:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我姑媽艾斯特的惡習都用這個治好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My aunt Esther cured all her habits with this--
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.75,0:40:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,液體抗腹瀉劑  治你的...那個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}liquid anti-diarrheal for the--well, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.51,0:40:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,檸檬和鹽補充電解質\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lemon and salt for the electrolytes,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.99,0:40:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解充血藥止鼻涕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}decongestant for the runny nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.88,0:40:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這都第三杯了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the third one.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.87,0:40:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再來七杯  你就精神煥發了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seven more, you'll be good as new.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.58,0:40:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去把車開過來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna go pull the van around.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.90,0:40:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他繼續喝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Make sure he keeps chugging those.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.03,0:40:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.59,0:40:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不客氣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.85,0:40:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又見了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello again.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.66,0:40:47.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好幾沒...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Long time no...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.57,0:40:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做我們做的事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}whatever it is we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.21,0:40:53.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你了  你去哪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I missed you. Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.27,0:40:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你走開了  還是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you leave, or did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.97,0:41:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許我們都走開了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe it was both.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.68,0:41:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也或者都沒  無所謂了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or neither. Doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.38,0:41:30.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些充滿希望的時刻嚇到我了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did those hopeful moments scare me?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.98,0:41:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了  后臺程序  記得嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course. Daemons, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.17,0:41:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早晚  會有一項"無需用戶操作程序"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At some point an "action without user interaction"
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.15,0:41:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出現  讓我措手不及\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}will come along and sweep my legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.78,0:41:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虛高真低的轉盤會繼續轉動\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This spinning wheel of false highs and true lows will continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.50,0:41:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這我確定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That much I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.46,0:43:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后臺程序  他們不會停止運轉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Daemons-- they don't stop working.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.38,0:44:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們總是活躍的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're always active.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.07,0:44:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們誘惑  操控\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They seduce. They manipulate.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.78,0:44:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們主宰我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They own us.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.95,0:44:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡管你在我身邊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And even though you're with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.00,0:44:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡管我創造了你  也無所謂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}even though I created you, it makes no difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.17,0:44:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都得獨自面對他們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We all must deal with them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.23,0:44:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們最多只能期望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The best we can hope for--
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.18,0:44:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一切之中唯一的希望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the only silver lining in all of this--
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.54,0:44:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我們撐過去時\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is that when we break through,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.66,0:44:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會看到有幾個熟人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we find a few familiar faces
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.41,0:44:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那邊等我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}waiting on the other side.
